      %h1 Meetups
      %p Our meetups are open to all experience levels, from total novices to expert Rubyists.

      .vevent
        %h2.summary BR-5: Build Conf Special

        %h3.when-icon.icon When?
        %p
          %span.dtstart
            - date_string = '2012-11-14'
            - date = Date.parse date_string
            %abbr.value{ :title => "#{date_string}" } #{date.strftime("#{date.day.ordinalize} %B, %Y")}
            %span.value 5:00pm

        %h3.where-icon.icon
          Where?
          %a.get-directions{ :href => "https://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=&hl=en&ie=UTF8&layer=c&daddr=The+Rumble+Laboratory+%4054.59289,-5.929398", :title => "Rumble Laboratory"} Get Directions
          
        %p.location
          The Rumble Laboratory
          %br
          2nd Floor, 21 Ormeau Avenue, Belfast, BT2 8HD

        %h3.what-icon.icon What?
        %p.description
          A special, 
          %a{:href => 'http://buildconf.com/'} Build Conf 
          Belfast Ruby event will be taking place on Wednesday 14th November. Weâ€™ve managed to convince a few awesome Rubyists attending Build to come do some lightning talks (5-10 minutes). The lineup is still being finalised but confirmed so far we have 
          %a{:href => 'https://twitter.com/elliottkember'} Elliott Kember, 
          %a{:href => 'https://twitter.com/zachinglis'} Zach Inglis 
          and 
          %a{:href => 'https://twitter.com/jasoncale'} Jason Cale. 
